 :installed-by "claude-9"
 :installed-at "2026-05-21"
 :registry-purpose
 "Operator-readable index of every cron job the futon stack relies on.
  Pair with `crontab -l` to verify the live schedule matches this registry.
  Mirror in the authoritative Futon1b substrate at hyperedge type
  `arxana/index/cron-jobs`."

